A production-grade Retrieval-Augmented Generation system built with Python, FastAPI, and OpenAI CLIP for multimodal semantic search over IIT Madras TDS course pages and Discourse forum threads.

- Playwright-based scraping pipeline that dynamically extracts and indexes JS-rendered content from course pages and Discourse.
- Intelligent text chunking at logical boundaries, embedded with ChromaDB + OpenAI CLIP — improving retrieval accuracy and answer quality over baseline approaches.
- Dual LLM API failover mechanism (OpenRouter → AI Pipe) with automatic fallback for high availability under rate limits or provider downtime.
